Name Errors/Static/JavaCompilation
Synopsis Compilation of generated Java code failed.
Description Some parts of the Rascal system generate Java code. Most notable is the parser generator. This error message is generated when the compilation of generated Java code fails.

Remedy: Contact the Rascal developers:
  • Ask a question at Rascal Ask site.
  • Read the currently open issues at the Rascal's issue tracker. If your problem has not yet been reported by someone else, please report it here.
